relationships between <IMG
 WIDTH="53" HEIGHT="37" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img49.png"
 ALT="$M(A)$"> and the <EM>centralizer algebra</EM>
<BR><P></P>
<DIV ALIGN="CENTER">
<!-- MATH
 \begin{displaymath}
C(A):={\rm End}_{A}{(V)}=\{ \mu \in {\cal E}|\; [\mu , \nu]=0, \;\mbox{ for
all } \nu \in A\}
\end{displaymath}
