all } \nu \in A\} \end{displaymath}">
</DIV>
<BR CLEAR="ALL">
<P></P>
we give a presentation of <IMG
 WIDTH="53" HEIGHT="37" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img49.png"
