<BR>
<P>
The residue classes of the
basis elements <!-- MATH
 ${{e}^*_{i}}^{j}$
 -->
<IMG
 WIDTH="28" HEIGHT="41" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img51.png"
 ALT="${{e}^*_{i}}^{j}$"> with respect to any coideal in <IMG
 WIDTH="24" HEIGHT="18" ALIGN="BOTTOM" BORDER="0"
